#### Step 1: Adding them to ~/.bashrc directly.
```sh
# KWORK definitions.
# You may want to put all your additions into a separate file like
# ~/.bashrc, instead of adding them here directly.
#####################KWORK#####################
export KWORK=~/kwork

if [ -f $KWORK/.bash_kwork ]; then
    . $KWORK/.bash_kwork
fi
#####################KWORK#####################
```
